The Bisasar Landfill Site will be terminating some of its
operations from Sunday, May 1, said eThekwini Municipality. The municipality said the site will only accept rubble and sand
cover material. All commercial customers are advised to dispose of garden
waste at any of the following landfill sites: ?             Marianhill
Landfill Site: Accepts only garden waste, rubble, and sand cover material.  (Strictly accounts only) ?             North –
Buffelsdraai Landfill Site (Strictly account only). ?             South –
Lovu Landfill Site (Strictly account only). Customers are advised to consider the landfill charges and
the implication to their business operations and related charges. For enquires contact the DSW Helpline on 031 311 8804.